- ğŸ¤– **Multi-Agent Collaboration**: AI agents perform specialized tasks such as resolving support inquiries and reviewing responses.
- ğŸ” **Web Scraping Integration**: Automatically pulls info from trusted sources like [CrewAI Docs](https://crewai.com/docs/introduction).
- ğŸ’¬ **Natural, Friendly Tone**: Outputs are helpful, casual yet professional â€” ideal for real-world support environments.
- ğŸ§  **Memory-Enabled CrewAI**: Agents can retain shared memory to improve task performance.
- ğŸ§© **Modular Architecture**: Easily extend or modify the system to include more agents or tools.

