## ğŸ› ï¸ Installation & Setup

1. Clone the repository  

    git clone https://github.com/saadtoorx/multi-agent-customer-support.git  
    cd multi-agent-customer-support  

2. Install dependencies  

    pip install -r requirements.txt  

3. Add your OpenAI API key by creating a `.env` file:  

    OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here  

---

## â–¶ï¸ Running the App

    streamlit run app.py

- ğŸ“ App simulates a support inquiry from a fictional customer.  
- ğŸ§  CrewAI kicks off task execution between agents.  
- ğŸ“‹ Final, polished response is displayed in Streamlit UI.  

